@node Introduction

	First of all, I would like the readers to excuse my poor English. I am French and it took me a lot of time to write this English documentation. So please be indulgent with me.
	SmallGrabber is a screen grabber. With its GUI, you can choose between lot of options. I tested it with most of the screenmodes and from 4 to 256 colors. So I think it will work on most the Amiga's. But, if you find some bugs, please contact me. I hope you will like SmallGrabber, 
	Sincerely,		@{"Mathieu Chenebit" LINK Auteur}

				@{"Main Page" LINK MAIN} 
@endnode
